    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Gaidulfus">Ghaiolfo</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Tanifredus">Tanifridi</name></persName>
                        riceve da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>
                        gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine ecc. (…), casa et res
                        illa in loco ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/584">Carsiana</placeName>,
                        pertenentes ecclesie vestre <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70"
                            key="#Churches">Sancti Fridiani</orgName>, qui est de subpotestatem
                        ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas ego ipsi ad manus meas abuit; casa vero ipsa cum
                        fundamento et edeficio suo, curte, orto, terris, vineis, silvis, virgareis,
                        pratis, pascuis, cultas res vel incultas, omnia quantum (…) mea portionem in
                        integrum mihi eas dedisti (…). Obbligo: ego vel meis heredes in ipsa casa
                        residere et abitare debeamus et tam ipsa casa et res quas mihi dedisti bene
                        laborare et gubernare seo meliorare debeamus et nobis eas privato nomine
                        usufructuandum (…). Censo: pro omni censum et iustitiam exinde tibi vel ad
                        successoribus tuis ad pars ipsius ecclesie Sancti Fridiani per singulos
                        annos, in mense decembrio, censum vobis dare debeamus, hic <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitate</rs> Luca ad ipsa ecclesia Sancti Fridiani, per nos aut per
                        misso nostro, vobis vel ad ministeriale vestro (…) argentum denarios bonos
                        expendiviles numero quattuor; et a mandato vestro venire debeamus hic Luca
                        legem et iustitiam faciendum tantum (…). Pena: spondeo cum meis heredes
                        conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos […] (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:
                            <persName ref="#people/150" key="#Witness">Fraolmi</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildiprandus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Donatus">Donatus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ardemannus"
                            >Ardimanno</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
